<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>When I run the core unit tests on a machine with no connexion to the Internet, I get 21 errors from the Gdata unit tests, just because it cannot connect to <a>www.google.com:80</a>.</p>

<p>I think that these tests should be enabled through a flag (TESTS_ZEND_GDATA_ENABLED), and this flag should be set to false in TestConfiguration.php.dist.</p>

